name: PersonalUseAutomationProject
description:
This project ask the user to choose a stock asset, it access the yahoo finace page and downloads the historical data of that asset.
 
-It formats the data by removing empty rows, removing strings and saving the file into an excel and comma seperated file (Symbol.xlsx and  Symbol.csv) 
-Sorts the input and output files into their respective folders
-All Symbol.csv files will be moved into Data/input folder

-The Symbol.xlsx will be stored in the project folder, if there is a new Symbol.csv file, the old one will be moved into Data/Output folder and the created Symbol.csv file will be in the Data/Ouput
